The paper deals with image recognition, which is a core topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of hierarchical prototypes and taxonomical organization of class labels suggests that the paper may also belong to the sub-category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The interpretability aspect of the model may also make it relevant to natural language processing (cs.CL) and neural networks (cs.NE).
